cast.overview: Humbert Humbert is a middle-aged British novelist who is both appalled by and attracted to the vulgarity of American culture. When he comes to stay at the boarding house run by Charlotte Haze, he soon becomes obsessed with Lolita, the woman's teenaged daughter.
cast.title: Lolita

details.biography: Erin Jane Dean is an American actress. She is best known for her lead role as Robbie Stevenson in the television series The Journey of Allen Strange. She has also appeared as the lead actress in Lovers Lane, and in a supporting role as Mona in Lolita. On television, she has appeared in episodes of Boy Meets World, A Pig's Tale, Monty, Against the Grain, and Nickelodeon's game show Figure It Out.
details.name: Erin J. Dean
